text: Don Campbell (born 16 February 1975) is a Caymanian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Caymanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Cayman Islands Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
